To be clear, in this retrospective cohort study *everyone* was vaccinated. Thus prior #SARSCoV2 infection was similar to getting a booster in terms of antibody response. 

(Ab titers from prior #SARSCoV2 infection alone are << titers from #CovidVaccine!)

Me:any reason you haven't got the #CovidVaccine?

Dad: No
Me:Will you get it?
Dad:No
